<div class="govuk-inset-text govuk-!-margin-top-4">
  <p class="govuk-body">
    <strong>Good news:</strong> The core platform you've just tested is production-ready. The checklist items are about integrating PlanX into your council's existing infrastructure, local planning policies, and data — not rebuilding the system.
  </p>
